datasets.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Cordless Phones
datasets.description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 2.2 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Telephony (cordless phones) that are effective as of November 1, 2008. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=phones.pr_crit_phones
